N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 341.7 - Eligibility

State Regulations

Any representative from a member institution or organized
student group or an alternate for a representative selected in accordance with
section
341.5
(d) of this

Part must be a student enrolled for credit who is included in a campus FTE base
and meets the campus' requirements to stand for election and continues to be
eligible to serve on the campus student government
organization. Notes
